Subject: Enron's financial position

Colleagues,

I want to assure all employees that Enron's balance sheet remains strong.
The write-downs announced this week relate to specific merchant investments
and the unwinding of some partnership structures including the Raptor vehicles.

The transactions involving LJM Cayman, Whitewing Associates, and Osprey Trust
are being reviewed. Greg Whalley and Jeff Skilling are working with advisors
to clarify the accounting treatment.

Enron stock remains a strong buy. I have personally purchased additional shares.

Kenneth Lay
